<p>Use three registers as operand to do logic operation</p>

<p>For example</p>

<p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">$t0 &lt;- $s1 + $s2</code></p>

<p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">add $t0, $s1, $s2</code></p>

